      "comment": "SHORTY (7) was below best last time when fifth at this track but three back was a Grade 4/5 winner in the quickest time on the card at this track. Will find this more suitable and can atone. MAKE YOUR STAND (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (23.38) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Has a good record at this journey. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Warrants plenty of respect. PITMAN GO QUICK (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Tarawi Banjo (30.73) in a Grade 5. Can measure up this time. MISS CRAWLEY (5) looks an each-way chance.",
